Paula Trickey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paula_Trickey 0 Paula Trickey (born March 27, 1966) is an American actress. She is known for her role as Cory McNamara on the USA Network series Pacific Blue (1996–2000), and for her roles in a number of television films.
